<field_enc>:
0: Disable redirection
1: Enable redirection to the CPU queue
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Copy IPv6 multicast control frames (DIP equals FF02::/16) to the CPU extraction queue given by CPU_PROTO_QU_CFG.CPU_IP6_MC_CTRL_QU.
------------------------------
<field_enc>:
0: Disable copy
1: Enable copy to CPU queue
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Redirect MLD IPv6 frames to the CPU extraction queue given by CPU_PROTO_QU_CFG.CPU_MLD_QU.

Frames must fulfill the following criteria to be considered MLD frames:
